					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5627622#post-4304235</guid>
				<title>I Love This.</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5627622/jude-s-bizarre-adventure#post-4304235</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2019 15:48:01 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Qyooo</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>5448222</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>This sh*t was the reason I made an account here. The irreverent, honest, authentic quality of Gamers Against Weed, the humor, the characters &#8212; it all reminds of me the online communities I had growing up (and still have, albeit its with the people around me now). This speaks to me in a way the other stories don't. It's <em>real</em>, while also being stupidly funny at the same time. What a good group of stories. What a good GoI.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
